56:45.652 --> 56:49.000
Thank him ev’ry day.


56:52.192 --> 56:54.360
Jehovah will always bless us 


56:54.360 --> 56:56.695
when we go to him 
in prayer with our concerns. 


56:56.695 --> 56:58.698
Whatever the situation, 


56:58.698 --> 57:01.901
he can give us 
“the power beyond what is normal.” 


57:01.902 --> 57:04.537
And as we learned 
and practiced in this program, 


57:04.537 --> 57:08.240
we do our part by training 
our “power of reason” 


57:08.240 --> 57:11.010
with the principles 
from his written Word.


57:11.010 --> 57:13.145
Finally, 
we have greetings 


57:13.145 --> 57:16.382
from the Vesterålen islands, 
in Norway.


57:16.382 --> 57:19.485
These islands are home to 30,000 people 


57:19.485 --> 57:22.155
who enjoy the beautiful fjords, mountains, 


57:22.155 --> 57:24.890
and calm beaches.


57:24.890 --> 57:28.728
The 53 publishers 
in the Sortland Norwegian Congregation 


57:28.728 --> 57:33.533
preach in a territory that covers 
1,800 square kilometers, 


57:33.533 --> 57:37.000
or 695 square miles. 


57:38.237 --> 57:42.709
Their thorough witnessing takes them 
into the beautiful countryside, 


57:42.708 --> 57:44.710
as well as to the city of Sortland 


57:44.710 --> 57:47.647
for metropolitan public witnessing. 


57:47.647 --> 57:50.184
Each year, they organize trips 
to unassigned territory, 


57:50.183 --> 57:52.085
where they often meet people 


57:52.085 --> 57:55.000
who show deep respect for the Bible.


57:56.188 --> 57:57.923
One Saturday each month, 
after the ministry, 


57:57.923 --> 58:01.126
they gather to watch 
the JW Broadcasting program 


58:01.127 --> 58:03.295
and enjoy spending time together. 


58:03.295 --> 58:06.265
Progressive Bible studies 
and a Russian group 


58:06.265 --> 58:08.935
join them each week 
at their meetings. 


58:08.935 --> 58:11.070
We send our love 
and greetings 


58:11.070 --> 58:13.873
and thank them 
for their Christian love 


58:13.873 --> 58:16.000
and example of faith.


58:17.943 --> 58:19.945
Thank you for watching. 


58:19.945 --> 58:22.515
From the world headquarters 
of Jehovah’s Witnesses, 


58:22.515 --> 58:31.775
this is JW Broadcasting!

